snippet: Lexie Brown hit four 3-pointers and scored 24 points and No. 15 Duke used a 10-0 run to start the fourth quarter for a 69-54 win over No. 17 Kentucky on Wednesday night for the Blue Devils' eighth-straight win....
lead_paragraph: Lexie Brown hit four 3-pointers and scored 24 points and No. 15 Duke used a 10-0 run to start the fourth quarter for a 69-54 win over No. 17 Kentucky on Wednesday night for the Blue Devils' eighth-straight win.

headline.main: Brown Leads No. 15 Duke Women Past No. 17 Kentucky 69-54
